ts.support

Class TSEnvironmentRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • ts.support.TSEnvironmentRecord
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TSDeclarativeEnvironmentRecord, TSObjectEnvironmentRecord

    public abstract class TSEnvironmentRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    The super class for all Tscript environment records (ELS 10.2.1).

    The subclasses are:

    • declarative environment records
    • object environment records (not implemented yet)
